 

1) we need to install httpd software  ###   90-88 server 
# yum install httpd -y 

2) My plan is to put pht website so i am going to install php software 
# yum install php -y 

3) cd /var/www/html 
vi index.php 

<?php
print "Hi"
?>


4) Enable the services 
# systemctl enable httpd  --now 


